{
  "stem": "6837.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to meet in our house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had a nice social life socializing with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I got married, and I had nobody-- my sister wasn't here yet when I got married.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Strangers around me by my wedding, somebody who made a wedding as a gift.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And everybody came, you know, just to participate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I had my child, I didn't want to talk-- when they were little, I didn't want to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only when they asked me, how come we don't have grandparents?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I told them, they're not alive anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I didn't go in details.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't want to sadden them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my children knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even if I didn't talk, they know we are different.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they felt-- later they told me, they felt guilty that they have a better life than I had, and they have a better-- they have parents and they live-- And they were only friends and associated with children whose parents went through in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had-- they were more comfortable with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They felt they had the same as background as theirs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were closer to those children, which we didn't realize it then.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We thought everything is, you know, normal, the way children are supposed to be brought up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we tried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we missed our parents, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We couldn't share our happiness with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When my first child was born, I thought it was the greatest gift that I could have gotten, a normal, healthy baby after all I went through because I thought even if I survive, or I'm going to have a long disease, or I'm going to have something, which what I went through is going to leave a mark.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But thank god, it didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
